Summary:
On the movie information screen, there is a section for information about movie. When the user clicks on the information icon, nothing changes. However, when the user clicks on the text, the new pop-up window with information about movie is displayed.

Steps to reproduce:
1. Click on Feed button on the bottom of screen.
2. Click on the ‘Ant-Man’ movie.
3. Click on the information icon button in information section.
Result: Nothing has changed.